Package git.jluvisi.minigames

Class GamePlayer

Object
GamePlayer
public class GamePlayer
extends Object
Repersents a spigot player that can join a GameInstance. Once a player joins a GameInstance they are made into a GamePlayer. GamePlayer's are normal spigot players but with additional atrributes.
